### ========================================
### AVAILABILITY API
### ========================================

### Upsert Working Hours
POST {{baseUrl}}/availability/working-hours
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "doctorId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
  "day": "MONDAY",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "17:00"
}

### List Working Hours
GET {{baseUrl}}/availability/working-hours?doctorId=123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Delete Working Hours
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/availability/working-hours/MONDAY?doctorId=123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create Busy Block
# @name createBusyBlock
POST {{baseUrl}}/availability/busy-blocks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "doctorId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
  "startTime": "2024-05-01T12:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2024-05-01T13:00:00Z",
  "type": "LUNCH",
  "reason": "Lunch break"
}

### List Busy Blocks
GET {{baseUrl}}/availability/busy-blocks?doctorId=123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000&from=2024-05-01T00:00:00Z&to=2024-05-31T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Delete Busy Block
@busyBlockId = {{createBusyBlock.response.body.id}}
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/availability/busy-blocks/{{busyBlockId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### List Slots
GET {{baseUrl}}/availability/slots?doctorId=123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000&date=2024-05-01&slotMinutes=30
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Validate Slot
POST {{baseUrl}}/availability/slots/validate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "doctorId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
  "startTime": "2024-05-01T10:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2024-05-01T10:30:00Z"
}
